{"tid":1478622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港好多人鍾意狗，西方社會更加唔使講，可唔可以唔好再以狗嚟鬧人","createTime":"2019-08-16T14:58:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T15:47:09.000Z","uid":245813,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bbcd62868aab8d005b91b275d42fc676c4ec3af7","tid":1478622,"uid":245813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:58:47.000Z","msg":"見到有啲文宣圖將啲差佬畫成狗<br />\n講真我個人覺得唔係咁舒服<br />\n<br />\n喺文明社會，狗好多時係被視為人類嘅朋友<br />\n而狗嘅 &quot;loyalty&quot; 本身亦係一種正面嘅quality<br />\n用嚟形容啲差佬真係侮辱哂啲狗<br />\n<br />\n難聽啲講<br />\n我甚至覺得係咪得啲食狗肉嘅大陸人先會用狗嚟踩人？"},{"pid":"cc1e35916dbd1128a8529c98140db69aabba66b7","tid":1478622,"uid":158270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:09:01.000Z","msg":"建議畫成蛇蠍蛛膜，文化共通"},{"pid":"6379ab62088592f38283484a69982a2debdad5da","tid":1478622,"uid":108814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:09:11.000Z","msg":"老鼠 過街老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548e67510957c698be8d22e9c3c9729b8b2468de","tid":1478622,"uid":263809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:30:17.000Z","msg":"黑社會"},{"pid":"663688f143ca33865138a17a2b0831a45d2b6c3d","tid":1478622,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:42:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警渣</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d180ddb85d1562e402b8b78d639355acdc9e6cfe","tid":1478622,"uid":268855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:47:09.000Z","msg":"不能認同更多<br />\n<br />\n愛狗人上<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}